Letâ€™s build it together!"*

ğŸ“š Lesson Structure
Intro â€“ Recap Episode 2 (read-only MySQL).

Explanation â€“ Mutations in GraphQL, writing data.

Demo â€“ Add a addBook mutation connected to MySQL.

