  }
}
âœ… Login:

mutation {
  login(input: { username: "alice", password: "secret" }) {
    token
    user {
      id
      username
    }
  }
}
Copy the returned token and set it in HTTP headers in Apollo Sandbox:

{
  "Authorization": "your_jwt_token_here"
}
âœ… Try adding a book without a token â†’ should fail.
âœ… Try again with a token â†’ should succeed.

