ğŸ’» Step 1: Update Database (Optional)
If you donâ€™t already have a created_at column for sorting by date, letâ€™s add it:

ALTER TABLE books ADD COLUMN created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP;
